quran[11{c,v,t}:
12,53,"mein kuch apne nafs ki براءت nahi kar raha hon, nafs to badi par aksata hi hai ila yeh ke kisi par mere rab ki rehmat ho, be shak mera rab bara ghafoor o Raheem hai """
12,54,"badshah ne kaha"" unhen mere paas lao taakay mein un ko apne liye makhsoos kar lon"" jab yousuf ne is se guftagu ki to is ne kaha"" ab aap hamaray haan qader o manzilat rakhtay hain aur aap ki amanat par poora bhrosa hai """
12,55,"yousuf ne kaha,"" malik ke khazanay mere supurd kiijiye, mein hifazat karne wala bhi hon aur ilm bhi rakhta hon """
12,56,"iss terhan hum ne uss sarzamen mein yousuf ke liye Iqtidaar ki raah hamwar ki woh mukhtaar tha ke is mein jahan chahay apni jagah banaye hum apni rehmat se jis ko chahtay hain nawaazte hain, naik logon ka ajar hamaray haan mara nahi jata"
12,57,aur akhirat ka ajar unn logo n ke liye ziyada behtar hai jo imaan le aeye aur khuda tarsi ke sath kaam karte rahay
12,58,yousuf ke bhai misar aeye aur is ke haan haazir hue is ne inhen pehchan liya magar woh is se na aashna thay
12,59,"phir jab is ne un ka samaan tayyar karwa diya to chaltay waqt un se kaha,"" apne soutelay bhai ko mere paas lana dekhte nahi ho ke mein kis terhan pemana bhar kar deta hon aur kaisa acha mehman Nawaz hon"
12,60,"agar tum usay nah lao ge to mere paas tumahray liye koi ghalla nahi hai balkay tum mere qareeb bhi nah phatakna """
12,61,"unhon ne kaha,"" hum koshish karen ge ke waalid sahib usay bhejnay par razi ho jayen, aur hum aisa zaroor karen ge """
12,62,"yousuf ne apne ghulamoo ko ishara kya ke"" inn logon ne ghallay ke aiwz jo maal diya hai woh chupkay se un ke samaan hi mein rakh do"" yeh yousuf ne iss umeed par kya ke ghar poanch kar woh apna wapas paaya howa maal pehchan jayen ge ( ya iss Fayazi par ahsaan mand hon ge ) aur ajab nahi ke phir pultayn"
12,63,"jab woh apne baap ke paas gay to kaha"" abba jaan, aindah hum ko ghalla dainay se inkaar kar diya gaya hai, lehaza aap hamaray bhai ko hamaray sath bhaij degiye taakay hum ghalla le kar ayen aur is ki hifazat ke hum zimma daar hain """
